on Z_{11}, (7^{-1} `mod` 11) is equal to (8 `mod` 11) and
  (3%7) |-> (3 * (7^{-1} `mod` 11) `mod` 11)
             == (3*8 `mod` 11) 
             == 2 ` mod 11

  *Ffield Data.Ratio> modp q 11
  2

